    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the style of painting popular in the early 1960's in Paris, London and New York. Reacting against Absract Expressionism, the style is characterized by a return of figurative images.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
